(188, 2, '2016-08-26 19:25:52', '2016-08-26 16:25:52', '<h3>История проекта</h3>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2><strong><span id="result_box" lang="ru"><span class="hps">Приветствуем</span> В<span class="hps">ас</span> <span class="hps">в разделе</span> <span class="hps">истории</span> <span class="hps">книжного</span> <span class="hps atn">проекта «</span>Читайка»!</span></strong></h2>\r\n<h3><strong><span lang="ru"> </span></strong></h3>\r\n<span id="result_box" lang="ru"><span class="hps">Книжный</span> <span class="hps">магазин</span> <span class="hps">«Читайка</span>» на Петровке <span class="hps">открылся</span>  <span class="hps">25 декабря 2009</span> года.  </span><span class="hps">Магазин</span> <span class="hps">расположен</span> <span class="hps">на расстоянии 100 метров</span><span class="hps">от станции</span> <span class="hps">метро</span> <span class="hps atn">«</span>Петровка» прямо на территории <span class="hps">книжного рынка.  </span><span id="result_box" lang="ru"><span class="hps">В</span> <span class="hps">ассортименте</span> <span class="hps">более</span> <span class="hps">20 000</span> <span class="hps">наименований</span> <span class="hps">книг и он </span><span class="hps">пополняется</span> <span class="hps">еженедельно!  </span></span><span id="result_box" lang="ru"><span class="hps">Интернет</span> <span class="hps">-магазин</span> <span class="hps">www.chytayka.com.ua</span> <span class="hps">работает в</span> <span class="hps">круглосуточном</span> <span class="hps">режиме</span>, <span class="hps">заказ</span>ы<span class="hps">оформляются</span> с понедельника по пятницу<span class="hps"> с</span> <span class="hps">09:00 до</span> <span class="hps">18:00.</span></span><span id="result_box" lang="ru"><span class="hps">  </span></span><span class="hps">Действует</span> <span class="hps">доставка по</span> <span class="hps">Киеву и</span> <span class="hps">Украине</span>.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-170" src="http://iter-design.dev/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/IMG_20140506_114443.jpg" alt="IMG_20140506_114443" />\r\n\r\n<span id="result_box" lang="ru"><strong><span class="hps">В</span> <span class="hps">ассортименте</span> <span class="hps atn">магазина «</span>Читайка» вы <span class="hps">найдете:</span></strong></span>\r\n\r\n<span id="result_box" lang="ru">\r\n<span class="hps">•</span> <span class="hps">современную</span> <span class="hps">и</span> <span class="hps">классическую</span> <span class="hps">художественную литературу</span>;\r\n<span class="hps">•</span> <span class="hps">детские</span> <span class="hps">книги;</span>\r\n<span class="hps">•</span> <span class="hps">книги</span> <span class="hps">для</span> <span class="hps">досуга</span> <span class="hps atn">(</span>фото, <span class="hps">путешествия</span>, <span class="hps">искусство</span>, <span class="hps">рыбалка, охота</span> <span class="hps">и</span> <span class="hps">др</span> <span class="hps">..</span>);\r\n<span class="hps">•</span> <span class="hps">литературу</span> <span class="hps">бизнес-направления</span>;\r\n<span class="hps">•</span> <span class="hps">книги по психологии</span> <span class="hps">и</span> <span class="hps">философии</span>;\r\n<span class="hps">•</span> <span class="hps">подарочные</span> <span class="hps">издания;</span>\r\n<span class="hps">•</span> <span class="hps">компьютерную</span> <span class="hps">литературу</span>;\r\n<span class="hps">•</span> <span class="hps">подарочные</span> <span class="hps">сертификаты</span>;\r\n<span class="hps">•</span> <span class="hps">аксессуары</span> <span class="hps">для</span> <span class="hps">книг.</span></span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class="alignleft wp-image-172 size-medium" src="http://iter-design.dev/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Untitled-3-600x424.jpg" alt="Untitled-3" width="600" height="424" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<h2><img class="alignleft wp-image-171 size-medium" src="http://iter-design.dev/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/IMG_4168-600x400.jpg" alt="IMG_4168" width="600" height="400" /></h2>\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<h2><strong><span id="result_box" lang="ru"><span class="hps"><a name="missia"></a>Миссия</span> <span class="hps">и ценности</span> <span class="hps">магазина</span> <span class="hps">«Читайка</span>»</span></strong></h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span id="result_box" lang="ru">\r\n<span class="hps">Перед</span> <span class="hps">книгой</span> <span class="hps">все равны</span>. <span class="hps">Чтение</span> <span class="hps">может</span> <span class="hps">объединять людей</span>, <span class="hps">давать новые</span> <span class="hps">темы</span> <span class="hps">для общения</span>, <span class="hps">новые мысли</span> <span class="hps">для осмысления</span>, <span class="hps">делать жизнь</span> <span class="hps">более</span> <span class="hps">интенсивным</span> <span class="hps">и</span> <span class="hps">захватывающим</span>, <span class="hps">а может и</span> <span class="hps">успокоить</span>. </span><span id="result_box" lang="ru"><span class="hps">Каждый раз</span>, <span class="hps">когда вы</span> <span class="hps">откладываете</span> <span class="hps">в сторону</span> <span class="hps">книгу и</span> <span class="hps">начинаете</span> <span class="hps">осмысливать</span> <span class="hps">прочитанное</span> <span class="hps">-</span> <span class="hps">книга</span> <span class="hps">достигла своей</span> <span class="hps">цели.</span></span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span id="result_box" lang="ru"><span class="hps">Владимир</span> <span class="hps">Набоков</span> <span class="hps">замечал:</span> <em><span class="hps atn">«</span>Литература <span class="hps">- это любовь</span> <span class="hps">к людям»</span>. </em></span><span class="hps">Умберто</span> <span class="hps">Эко</span> <span class="hps">говорил</span>, <span class="hps">что прочитать</span> <span class="hps">все</span> <span class="hps">выдающиеся</span> <span class="hps">мировые</span> <span class="hps">книги</span> <span class="hps">есть возможность</span> <span class="hps">у каждого</span>, <span class="hps">в то время как</span> <span class="hps">у одного человека</span> <span class="hps">нет физической возможности</span> <span class="hps">посетить все</span> <span class="hps">страны мира.</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span id="result_box" lang="ru"><span class="hps">Книги</span> <span class="hps">- это</span> <span class="hps">чудо</span>. <span class="hps">Белые</span> <span class="hps">страницы</span> <span class="hps">или</span> <span class="hps">цветные</span>, <span class="hps">черные</span> <span class="hps">буквы</span> <span class="hps">или</span> <span class="hps">синие</span>, <span class="hps">но</span> <span class="hps">в каждой книге</span> <span class="hps">прячутся</span> <span class="hps">новые</span> <span class="hps">миры</span> <span class="hps">и</span> <span class="hps">новые друзья.</span></span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span id="result_box" lang="ru"><span class="hps">По крайней мере</span>, <span class="hps">мы в этом</span> <span class="hps">уверены...  ;-)</span></span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3><strong>Наша цель</strong></h3>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nКнига – это источник знаний и элемент досуга. Мы помогаем людям найти актуальные интересные книги для досуга или развития, подобрать книги для детей, найти подарок для коллеги или друга.  Главная наша цель -   <span class="hps">создать лучший </span><span class="hps">в </span><span class="hps">Украине </span><span class="hps">магазин и </span><span class="hps">интернет</span><span class="atn">-</span>магазин <span class="hps">книг </span><span class="hps">для людей</span>, <span class="hps">которые </span><span class="hps">не представляют </span><span class="hps">своей жизни </span><span class="hps">без </span><span class="hps">ежедневного </span><span class="hps">чтения! </span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span id="result_box" lang="ru">\r\n<span class="hps">Каждый год мы</span> <span class="hps">внедряем</span> <span class="hps">инновации</span>, <span class="hps">улучшаем</span> <span class="hps">сервисы</span> <span class="hps">и</span> <span class="hps">расширяем</span> <span class="hps">ассортимент</span>,  п<span class="hps">олучаем</span> <span class="hps">высокие оценки</span> <span class="hps">нашей работы</span>, <span class="hps">хорошие отзывы</span> <span class="hps">от поставщиков</span> <span class="hps">и</span> <span class="hps">партнеров.</span>  <strong><span class="hps">Мы</span> <span class="hps">верим</span>, <span class="hps">что</span> <span class="hps">развитие и совершенствование</span> <span class="hps">- это</span> <span class="hps">путь, ведущий</span> <span class="hps">к успеху!</span></strong></span>\r\n\r\n<strong><span id="result_box" lang="ru">\r\n<span class="hps">Почему</span> <span class="hps">покупать книги</span> <span class="hps atn">в «</span>Читайке» <span class="hps">удобно</span> <span class="hps">и</span> <span class="hps">приятно</span>?</span></strong>\r\n\r\n<span id="result_box" lang="ru">\r\n<span class="hps"><strong>1</strong>.</span> <strong><span class="hps">Широкий</span> <span class="hps">ассортимент</span> <span class="hps">книг</span></strong></span>\r\n\r\n<span id="result_box" lang="ru">\r\n<span class="hps">Мы</span> <span class="hps">избавим</span> <span class="hps">вас от</span> <span class="hps">поисков -</span> <span class="hps">у нас в</span> <span class="hps">магазине</span> <span class="hps">находится более</span> <span class="hps">20 000</span> <span class="hps">наименований</span> <span class="hps">книг.</span> <span class="hps">Мы</span> <span class="hps">работаем</span> <span class="hps">с</span> <span class="hps">более</span> <span class="hps">чем 750</span><span class="hps">издательствами</span> <span class="hps">Украины</span> <span class="hps">и России.</span></span>\r\n\r\n<span id="result_box" lang="ru">\r\n<strong><span class="hps">2.</span> <span class="hps">Профессиональная</span> <span class="hps">консультация</span></strong></span>\r\n\r\n<span id="result_box" lang="ru">\r\n<span class="hps">Обратившись</span> <span class="hps">к нам</span>, <span class="hps">вы гарантированно</span> <span class="hps">получите</span> <span class="hps">профессиональную</span> <span class="hps">консультацию</span> <span class="hps">и обслуживание</span>. <span class="hps">Помочь в</span> <span class="hps">выборе</span> <span class="hps">-</span><span class="hps">наша обязанность.</span></span>\r\n\r\n<span id="result_box" lang="ru">\r\n<strong><span class="hps">3</span>. <span class="hps">Оперативная</span> <span class="hps">доставка</span></strong></span>\r\n\r\n<span id="result_box" lang="ru">\r\n<span class="hps">Мы максимально</span> <span class="hps">оперативно</span> <span class="hps">доставим</span> <span class="hps">Ваш заказ</span>:\r\n<span class="hps">•</span> <span class="hps">по</span> <span class="hps">Киеву -</span> <span class="hps">в течение суток</span>;\r\n<span class="hps">•</span> <span class="hps">по</span> <span class="hps">Украине</span> <span class="hps">Новой</span> <span class="hps">Почтой</span> <span class="hps">- в течение</span> <span class="hps">1-2 суток</span>;\r\n</span>\r\n\r\n<span id="result_box" lang="ru"><span class="hps">Бесплатно</span> <span class="hps">доставим</span> <span class="hps">по</span> <span class="hps">Киеву и по</span> <span class="hps">Украине</span> <span class="hps">при</span> <span class="hps">заказе</span> <span class="hps">на</span> <span class="hps">сумму</span> <span class="hps">400</span> <span class="hps">грн</span>.</span>\r\n\r\n<span id="result_box" lang="ru">\r\n<strong><span class="hps">4.</span> <span class="hps">Бонусная программа для</span> <span class="hps">покуп